{
  "id": "adv_event_2201_01_05",
  "title": "初日の出の\n太陽のように",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "駅員さんに聞いてきたけど\n東京方面の電車は全て止まっているそうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I asked the station staff. They say that all\ntrain services towards Tokyo are suspended.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.614240264899999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.8075734456
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "ネットでもニュースになってる……\nシステム障害で運転再開はいつになるか分からない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s all over the Internet too.\nThere’s a system fault and nobody knows when the trains will start again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8075734456,
      "endTime": 14.7758955319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.9692286173
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしよう……\nこのままじゃライブに間に合わないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What shall we do?\nWe won’t make it in time for the live like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9692286173,
      "endTime": 19.8521763483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないわ、電車は諦めてタクシーを拾いましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We should give up on the train and take a taxi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.0588428814,
      "endTime": 24.958842785999998,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5113.333209400001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.1721760908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "でもタクシー乗り場、凄い人……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the taxi rank is so crowded.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.1721760908,
      "endTime": 28.3789787451,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7127.823909199997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.5789788405
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、バスを乗り継いで行けば……\nって、バス停も凄い人だかりだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ if we take the buses…\nAh‚ the bus stop is mobbed too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5789788405,
      "endTime": 35.866461865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.0531285126
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく並ぶしかないよ\nでも、これで間に合うのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ we just need to get in line.\nBut will that get us there in time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0531285126,
      "endTime": 42.001835902399996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.1951691309
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "一体どうしたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should we do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1951691309,
      "endTime": 44.5287065187,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2540.2040638999993
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.7353731948
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、電話だ\n……{user}さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ my phone’s ringing.\n…{user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7353731948,
      "endTime": 48.4848515826,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 500
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし、ちょうど良かったです\n電車が止まっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ that’s perfect timing.\nThe trains have stopped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6981849351,
      "endTime": 53.5110418954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.6977085906
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　ニュースで見たから知ってる？\nだから助っ人をこっちに向かわせた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you saw it on the news?\nSo you’ve got a helper heading to us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.6977085906,
      "endTime": 60.708660872500005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.9153273104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "助っ人ってどういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What does he mean by a “helper”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9153273104,
      "endTime": 64.0435586451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.230225245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "よく分からないけど\n{user}さんが駅前で待ってろって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not sure.\n{user}-san said to wait in front of the station.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.230225245,
      "endTime": 69.5696811356,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4569.774754999998
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11330.108229399997
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11330.108229399997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.7763478595
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ねえみんな、あそこの車\nもの凄い勢いでこっちに向かって来てない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look at that car over there.\nIs it trying to reach us through the crowd?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7763478595,
      "endTime": 76.9690690355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.1624022164
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……って、ちょっと待って！\nこのままじゃぶつかる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… Oh‚ wait!\nIt’s going to hit us at this rate!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1624022164,
      "endTime": 82.53333333329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "きゃあぁぁぁっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eeeek!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7333333333,
      "endTime": 84.566757353,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "と、止まった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it stopped…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7666666667,
      "endTime": 87.35922891300001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　運転席にいるのって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? Look who’s in the driving seat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6,
      "endTime": 90.7869388103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせしましたぁ～！\nお迎えに参りましたよぉ～！　ささ、乗った乗ったぁ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for keeping you waiting!\nI came to pick you up! Quickly‚ hop in!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.9666666667,
      "endTime": 98.18725483360001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさん！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Satomi-san!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.3666666667,
      "endTime": 99.6923356454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさん、免許持ってたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve got a driver’s license‚ Satomi-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9,
      "endTime": 103.5843536377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_05-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "こう見えても運転にはちょ～っと自信あるっす！\nくぅー、このヒリつく感じ久しぶりっすねぇー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I may not look like it‚ but I’ve got some confidence as a driver.\nIt’s been a long time since I felt an ache like this!",
        "id": ""
      },
